p.k: Booty Eggs / TV Knight 4 / Teen Titans Roar! / What's Opera, Titans? Not wanting to be creeped out on Easter the Titans dispatch the Easter Bunny and take matters into their own hands. / Batman and Commissioner Gordon go camping but instead of fun outdoor activities they'd rather watch TV. / The Titans are outraged when their favourite cartoon is rebooted, so they come up with a plan to get this new show off the air. / Robin surprises the Titans with a trip to the opera, but they soon fall asleep, and all dream about starring in their own operas.
